tr.td: Adjusted size and position of cogwheel emblem

tr.td: Reverted to version as of 13:29, 14 September 2018 (UTC) Added multiple sources that confirm that the flag from 1975-1983 had this exact design and colour scheme, additionally the colour scheme for the flag changed well after the new flag was adopted and did not apply to the previous Mozambican flag.

img.alt: Thumbnail for version as of 18:51, 24 February 2019

tr.td: Reverted to version as of 22:36, 15 June 2018 (UTC): no source for previous version. For current version: [https://www.flagmakers.co.uk/flag-history/mozambique] ("Flagmakers"). Moreover, previous flag out of colors style and design compared to other Mozambique flags 1975-1983 (see: "en:Flag of Mozambique").

img.alt: Thumbnail for version as of 13:29, 14 September 2018

tr.td: Adjusted the emblem inside the cogwheel to be more historically accurate.

img.alt: Thumbnail for version as of 06:24, 11 August 2018

tr.td: Changed flag to fit former official version more properly

img.alt: Thumbnail for version as of 22:36, 15 June 2018

img.alt: Thumbnail for version as of 06:03, 29 April 2018

tr.td: Adjusted flags colours and coat of arms to fit the description laid out by the former constitution of Mozambique and also based off what the flag looked like in old photographs/videos.
